citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:47AM on March
2nd, 2022. A voicemail was left on the licensee's phone requesting a call back. The licensee texted back that she would
not be available for an inspection until the following week.
End Section
